thread.title: Judy Renaud
thread.title_full: Disc Makers reviewed by Judy Renaud

author: Judy Renaud
title: Judy Renaud
text: Can't thank Disc Makers enough for their help in all aspects of my two projects with them this year, "When Love Comes Around The Corner" & "Something Cool." From my knowing nothing about producing and distributing a recording to having two finalized products that are as professionally done as any recording out there and selling and streaming and looking good is the best feeling in the world. For all the rest of you out there that want to have your work out there or just something to leave behind like me, Disc Makers will help you make it happen for the right price and with all the help and support you need. Go for it!
